columnConfigurations.columnName: Early Deliveries compared to date in PO item (%)
columnConfigurations.columnAlias: Early Deliveries compared to date in PO item (%)

dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time till GR posted (days)",
    "Early Deliveries compared to date in PO item (%)",
    "Late Deliveries compared to date in PO item (%)",
    "Late GR postings (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Delivery items with goods receipt posted") 
        	AS "Time till GR posted (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery items with delivery date earlier than date in purchase order item") * 100 
        	AS "Early Deliveries compared to date in PO item (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery items with delivery date later than date in purchase order item") * 100 
        	AS "Late Deliveries compared to date in PO item (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Delivery items with goods receipt posting later than planned") * 100 
        	AS "Late GR postings (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
	GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
